@startuml
title AI-Assisted Feature Workflow

start
:Human describes feature;
:GameMaker assistant defines behavior;
:Update project documents and diagrams;
if (Milestone ready?) then (yes)
  :Create Codex implementation task;
  :Codex reads AGENTS.md and repository;
  :Codex implements smallest coherent change;
  :Human tests in GameMaker;
  :GameMaker assistant reviews diff and behavior;
  if (Fixes required?) then (yes)
    :Create correction task;
    --> :Codex reads AGENTS.md and repository;
  else (no)
    :Commit completed feature;
    stop
  endif
else (no)
  :Complete missing planning;
  --> :Update project documents and diagrams;
endif

@enduml
